reviewText: OMG....if you want to laugh out loud.....trust me, YOU MOST CERTAINLY WILL. Good ol Agnes Brown and the rest of the bunch will have you in stitches! My very favorite comedy shows. Can't get enough!
very funny will always love Mrs. Brown and her Dvd's, can't wait to purchase Da'Movie since I don't foresee it coming to the U.S theaters.

The actual delivery date was something of a surprise.  I had not expected it to take 2 months.  It was meant as a Christmas gift but did not arrive until the middle of January.  Other than that the product was fine and much enjoyed by the receiver.

GREAT ENTERTAINMENT , IF YOU LOVE TO LAUGH,BUY MRS. BROWNS BOYS ! YOU WILL NEVER REGRET BUYING THESE , JUST REMEBER YOU HAVE TO BUY A DVD THAT PLAYS REGION "B" DVDS! OR SET YOUR COMPUTER TO PLAY THEM AND ENJOY!
This is the funniest show I have ever watched, the scripts are fantastic, a good all year round show not just at Christmas, if u order this you won't be sorry.
love these.have the whole series. this one is a little more sentimental but still funny. so happy this one is new.

Absolute hysteria in one box. Is the only way i can describe this series I have laughed till I cried and then laughed more.
You will never look at a christmas special the same way again.  This whole series is just the best

I love the Mrs Brown's Boys series and I purchase every thing they have out.  I only wish they had more episodes and I wish that they were aired in the US.  But luckily I'm able to purchase the DVDs and enjoy them here in the US.  This is one of the funniest shows I have ever seen.
Mrs. Brown's boys had me at "bikini wax treatment" in Series 1.  This dvd shows the lovey dovey stuff a bit more, but it's still funny and a must have for the collection.
